From: Stanislav <shylostas.com@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 22 Jan 2026 18:00:00 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: Intel: soc-sdw: add quirk for Alienware 18 Area-51 AA18250

This patch adds a sound quirk for the Alienware 18 Area-51 AA18250 laptop
to enable internal speakers and the headset jack. Without these flags,
the SoundWire initialization fails due to a resource conflict.

Signed-off-by: Stanislav <shylostas.com@gmail.com>

--- a/sound/soc/intel/boards/sof_sdw.c
+++ b/sound/soc/intel/boards/sof_sdw.c
@@ -758,6 +758,16 @@ static const struct dmi_system_id sof_sdw_quirk_table[] = {
 		.driver_data = (void *)(SOC_SDW_CODEC_SPKR),
 	},
 	{
+		.callback = sof_sdw_quirk_cb,
+		.matches = {
+			DMI_MATCH(DMI_SYS_VENDOR, "Alienware"),
+			DMI_MATCH(DMI_PRODUCT_NAME, "Alienware 18 Area-51 AA18250"),
+		},
+		.driver_data = (void *)(SOC_SDW_CODEC_SPKR |
+					SOC_SDW_CODEC_MIC |
+					SOC_SDW_FOUR_SPK),
+	},
+	{
 		.callback = sof_sdw_quirk_cb,
 		.matches = {
 			DMI_MATCH(DMI_SYS_VENDOR, "Alienware"),